              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"React Frontend Developer\",\n  \"description\": \"Seeking a talented React Frontend Developer to build beautiful, responsive user interfaces. Required: 3+ years React experience, TypeScript, Next.js, Tailwind CSS. You should be comfortable with state management (Redux, Context API), REST APIs, and modern frontend best practices. Experience with performance optimization and unit testing with Jest is preferred. Join our team to build the future of AI-powered job matching!\"\n}"
