              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"DevOps Engineer\",\n  \"description\": \"Looking for a DevOps Engineer to manage and optimize our infrastructure. Required: Docker, Kubernetes, AWS/GCP, CI/CD pipelines. You will be responsible for deployment automation, monitoring, and maintaining our cloud infrastructure. Experience with Terraform, Jenkins, and Linux system administration is essential. Must have 3+ years of DevOps experience and strong problem-solving skills.\"\n}"
