              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Machine Learning Engineer\",\n  \"description\": \"Join our AI team as a Machine Learning Engineer. You will work on our embedding models and matching algorithms. Required: Strong Python skills, deep learning framework experience (TensorFlow/PyTorch), understanding of NLP and embeddings. You should have 2+ years of ML engineering experience, knowledge of model deployment and optimization. Bachelor's in Computer Science or related field preferred. This role involves building the brain of our job matching system!\"\n}"
